Text: "We all know the conflicts between Israel and the Palestine. Or do we? The media\
  \ and western governments have fed us a reality to different from the locals point\
  \ of view! As a traveller I live on the locals experience, their point of view and\
  \ opinions. As citizens of the world I find it necessary to know all reality\u2019\
  s and most importantly know them through the eyes of the indigenous population"
